reviewText: Why does this DVD only have two Mickey Rooney movies? The reason I gave it 2 stars was because of the 2 Mickey Rooney Movies
love all his movies i get from you

Very misleading DVD by Echo Bridge Entertainment. The Mickey Rooney Collection but only two of the eight movies contain Mickey Rooney??? What is wrong with this? I won't be buying anything made by Echo Bridge again!
Only two films have Mickey Rooney.
Unless he has a minor role in the other six, only two of the eight films feature Mickey Rooney.  Some commemoration!
